{"tid":2050786,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[DW] 地攤經濟：中國經濟新冠時代救星？","createTime":"2020-06-04T10:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T23:45:45.000Z","uid":179729,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"327c54a4f3d91baca9d2f51a570700450f791bfd","tid":2050786,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:40:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://dw.com/p/3dCsz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw.com%2Fp%2F3dCsz&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY8wCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=f32ded4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://dw.com/p/3dCsz</a><br />\n<br />\n地攤，這個承載著一代中國人記憶的東西幾近消失，如今又強勢回歸。隨著中國總理李克強一句它&quot;是人間的煙火&quot;，是&quot;是中國的生機&quot;。&quot;地攤經濟&quot;如今成為了中國各地政府恢復就業的政策法寶。但一些&quot;傷口&quot;未癒合的民眾，卻並不買賬。<br />\n<br />\n（德國之聲中文網）就在過去的20年間，小商小販們在中國各大城市擺攤叫賣的景象逐漸淡出的人們的視野。隨著中國近幾十年來的經濟飛速發展，各地政府爭先恐後推出形象工程。在讓城市&quot;亮起來&quot;的同時，承載著一代中國人記憶的雪糕、煎餅果子、麻辣燙攤鋪消失在了城市的車水馬龍和玻璃鋼鐵幕牆之間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHvos2W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHvos2W.png&h=5fe5af25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/m_wo8y/status/1267908101186809857?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fm_wo8y%2Fstatus%2F1267908101186809857%3Fs%3D20&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY8wCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=f2acab0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fm_wo8y%2Fstatus%2F1267908101186809857%3Fs%3D20&h=153bdb00\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/m_wo8y/status/1267908101186809857?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"940d09e79533f781b7e82e8e0e9dca2b412d83a6","tid":2050786,"uid":73281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:48:46.000Z","msg":"寧吃共產主義的草，也不走資本主義的回頭路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蠣螛了蛾的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d5142cab8119467e30831b5affcf9857a